newsitem.title: USA: U.S. soybean inspection destinations - USDA.
newsitem.headline: U.S. soybean inspection destinations - USDA.

text.p: The 33.430 million bushels of U.S. soybeans inspected for export in the week ended Nov 7 were for the following destinations (1,000 bushels):
Mississippi River to Belgium 1,816; China 5,728; Colombia 121; Denmark 345; Indonesia 1,213; Israel 571;Japan 916;S Korea 1,974; Malaysia 1,147; Holland 3,075; Spain 2,344; Turkey 223.
East Gulf to Mexico 808. North Texas to France 1,676. Columbia River to Philippines 809. Puget Sound to Malaysia 2,056. Interior to Mexico 634.
